                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-main);">
                    Ella Rises is dedicated to empowering Latina youth by providing them with the tools, mentorship,
                    and experiences needed to embrace their heritage and become leaders in their communities.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-main);">
                    We believe that when a young woman rises, she lifts her entire community with her. Through our
                    workshops and summits, we are building a network of strong, resilient, and ambitious women.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="zigzag-image">
                <img src="/img/ER UMFA Mural_049.jpg" alt="Community Mural">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

